  "body": "https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/pkg/kubelet/eviction/threshold_notifier_linux.go#L114\r\n\r\nclose it may make kubelet crash, though the possibility is small.\r\nkeep it open is just ok.\r\nAnd to avoid getThresholdEvents blocked for ever, stopCh should be passed in it.\r\n\r\n\r\n```golang\r\nfunc getThresholdEvents(eventfd int, eventCh chan<- int, stopCh <-chan struct{}) {\r\n\tfor {\r\n\t\tbuf := make([]byte, 8)\r\n\t\t_, err := syscall.Read(eventfd, buf)\r\n\t\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\t\treturn\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\tselect {\r\n\t\tcase eventCh <- 0:\r\n\t\tcase <-stopCh:\r\n\t\t\treturn\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n}\r\n```",
